"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-olympics-cardboard-box-poster-medal-paris-2024-b2587649.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Many viewers have been confused by the mysterious cardboard boxes handed out at the Olympics  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  The 2024 ParisOlympicsis well underway as the world's athletes continue to compete for gold in sports ranging from swimming to skateboarding.\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some events have already wrapped up, withTeam GBsecuringa few medals in the early days.\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 669, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But this year, the Paris Olympic organisers have thrown in a bonus prize for medal winners too: a mysterious cardboard box.\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 7.339592400666748e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some viewers have been confused to see these Olympians handed a long, thin cardboard box as they have the medals hung around their neck.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The box is yellow, and a roll of paper can be seen through its window.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a Paris-themed poster, specially made for this year's Olympics.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Designed by French artist Ugo Gattoni, the limited-edition illustration is being given as a special thanks to winning competitors.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1089, \"end\": 1095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9704071624097357, \"rank\": 0.020646608073524503, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The poster show a cartoon version of Paris, complete with a bright-red Eiffel Tower and the Seine.\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1246, \"end\": 1251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 7.339592400666748e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1301, \"end\": 1306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999955925887, \"rank\": 2.8268183064487024e-09, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sporting events are taking place all over the city centre as spectators watch on, seated in a giant stadium.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1416, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the front of the Eiffel Tower, you will see the words 'XXXIII Olympiade,' as this year's Olympics mark the 33rd edition of the games.\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It also has the words XXXIII Olympiade referencing the fact thatParis 2024is the 33rd edition of the Games.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_XXXIII\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, 