letes share their awards online and tell fans their plans for their posters.\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2330, \"end\": 2341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999999874944, \"rank\": 1.0748818643352025e-11, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"